{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": [{"tool_use_id": "chatcmpl-tool-85352fdd96520ad8", "type": "tool_result", "content": "# $τ$-Voice: Benchmarking Full-Duplex Voice Agents on Real-World Domains\narXiv: 2603.13686\nAuthors: Soham Ray, Keshav Dhandhania, Victor Barres, Karthik Narasimhan\nYear: 2026 | Venue: \nTopic: speech_agent\nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. A voice agent benchmark combining verifiable completion of complex grounded tasks, full-duplex interaction, and realistic audio.\n  2. A controllable and realistic voice user simulator with diverse accents, realistic audio environments, and rich turn-taking dynamics.\n  3. Empirical findings revealing a substantial voice-text gap where voice agents retain only 30-45% of text capability under realistic conditions.\n\nTags: Eval, Eval/基准, Eval/情感语境交互, Eval/安全性, Agent, Agent/对话型LALM", "is_error": false}]}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "3542bf67-0de4-4983-94f1-427e4f1c4661", "uuid": "52d246ee-62ec-4787-961b-4ef46afb77b1", "timestamp": "2026-07-21T13:09:07.469Z", "tool_use_result": {"stdout": "# $τ$-Voice: Benchmarking Full-Duplex Voice Agents on Real-World Domains\narXiv: 2603.13686\nAuthors: Soham Ray, Keshav Dhandhania, Victor Barres, Karthik Narasimhan\nYear: 2026 | Venue: \nTopic: speech_agent\nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. A voice agent benchmark combining verifiable completion of complex grounded tasks, full-duplex interaction, and realistic audio.\n  2. A controllable and realistic voice user simulator with diverse accents, realistic audio environments, and rich turn-taking dynamics.\n  3. Empirical findings revealing a substantial voice-text gap where voice agents retain only 30-45% of text capability under realistic conditions.\n\nTags: Eval, Eval/基准, Eval/情感语境交互, Eval/安全性, Agent, Agent/对话型LALM", "stderr": "", "interrupted": false, "isImage": false, "noOutputExpected": false}}
